      "id": "scenario_2b3_s1",
      "name": "Commission Both Circuits",
      "description": "Both MCCs are de-energised and all valves are closed. Commission the service circuit first (cooling side must flow before the process side enters the heat exchanger): open V_S1 → close SW_S_Iso — the shaft turns and P_Service auto-starts → open V_S2. Then commission the process circuit: open V_P1 → close SW_P_Iso — the shaft turns and P_Process auto-starts → open V_P2. Heat transfer becomes active when both sides flow.",
